node.text:
#ad Happy to announce that Angela and I partnered with @amazonca to surprise the Hometown Hero, Heather - a deserving and inspiring woman that has been committed to her work with @breakfastclubofcanada for more than 20 years - with a makeover and some surprises.
En plus, nous avons eu le plaisir de rencontrer Heather virtuellement lors d’un appel vidéo surprise! Elle connaît son hockey!
If you want to learn more about Heather’s amazing story, find behind the scenes footage, see the virtual surprise meeting, and explore products from the makeover (including Angela’s and my Amazon favourites), visit amazon.ca/hometownheroes #AmazonPartner #amazonhometownheroes #deliveringsmiles #amazoncanada

node.text:
#TheOutsideIsCalling. And whether it’s my backyard or the Canadian backcountry, @colemancanada_ is my trusted source for camping equipment. I’ve partnered with Coleman Canada to inspire more of you to answer the call of the outdoors. Because if there’s one place I’d be rather than on the ice, it’s in the Canadian outdoors. Coleman camping equipment is available at:
www.walmart.ca
